{"word":"H2442 - חָכָה - châkâh - khaw-kaw' - Long","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָכָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châkâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Long"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காத்திரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to wait, to wait for, to await"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to wait for"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to wait, to tarry"},{"paragraph":"2) to wait (in ambush)"},{"paragraph":"3) to wait for, to long for"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (apparently akin to <a href=\"#/H2707 - חָקָה - châqâh - khaw-kaw'/2707\">H2707</a> through the idea of <i>piercing</i>); properly to <i>adhere</i> to; hence to await: - long, tarry, wait."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}